# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  PaperTalker-CLI 环境配置
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── 代理（访问 Google NotebookLM 需要）──────────────────
HTTPS_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:7897
HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:7897

# ── NotebookLM 认证文件路径（可选，默认 ~/.notebooklm/storage_state.json）──
# NOTEBOOKLM_STORAGE_PATH=C:\Users\你的用户名\.notebooklm\storage_state.json

# ── 视频风格（可选，命令行 --style 优先）──────────────────
# VIDEO_STYLE=whiteboard

# ── 论文搜索 API Keys（可选，部分平台需要）──────────────
# NCBI_API_KEY=your_ncbi_api_key
# NCBI_EMAIL=your_email@example.com
# SS_API_KEY=your_semantic_scholar_api_key
